[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **WHY THIS WORKS:** Regex filters often case-sensitive, but parsers (HTML,   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m SQL) are case-insensitive.                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Dimension 3: WHITESPACE ALTERNATIVES                                     [34m│[0m
