[34m│[0m UTF-8 Overlong│ %c0%bc (for <)  │ %c0%ae (for .)  │                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Base64       │ PHNjcmlwdD4=     │ Li4vZXRjL3Bhc3N3ZA== │                     [34m│[0m
