[34m│[0m ### Context Detection Framework                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m STEP 1: IDENTIFY OUTPUT CONTEXT                                              [34m│[0m
