[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **KEY INSIGHT:** Filters decode at one layer, execution happens at another.  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - If filter checks URL-decoded but backend double-decodes → double-encode    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - If filter checks raw but backend URL-decodes → URL-encode                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Dimension 2: CASE TRANSFORMATIONS                                        [34m│[0m
